  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q008911.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Ninmarki , his lady , Piriĝ-me , his child , dedicated this ( human-faced bison ) for the well-being of Ur-Ninĝirsu , ruler of Lagaš , and for his own well-being ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q008911.11",
      "line_range": "11",
      "translation": "(11) The name of this ( object ) is \" The starving is the beloved of her heart \"."
    }
  ],
